quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"ЖҒen Й“e jortaaki hawroyde e Amen wi'i: \"Ko hannoo jippinee e makko Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en, maaЙ—um men yi'a Joomi amen?\" GomЙ—ii Й“ee mawnintinike ka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, Й“e townitii townitaare mawnunde"
  25,22,"Г‘alnde Й“e yi'oyta Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en weltaare alanaa bomЙ“e Й“en nden Г‘alnde, Й“e wi'a: \"Heedo heedaango"
  25,23,"Men ardini faade e ko Й“e gollunoo kon immorde e gollal, Men waЙ—i ngal punndi caraandi"
  25,24,YimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en nden Г‘alnde Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude ГұiiЙ“irde Й“uri labeede kadi Гұallirde
  25,25,E Г‘alnde nde kummu ngun seekorta duule Й—en Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en jippinee jippineede
  25,26,"Laamu GoongAawu ngun nden Г‘alnde ko Hinnorante On ngu woodani, laatoo Г‘alnde saЙ—tunde e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  25,27,"E Г‘alnde tooГұuЙ—o on ЕӢatoyta junngo makko ngon, o wi'a: \"Eeh jalla min, mi jogitino wonndude e NulaaЙ—o on Laawol"
  25,28,"Eeh bone am haaniino min, mi jogitanooki kaariijo sehilaajo"
  25,29,"GomЙ—ii o majjinii lam gaayi Deftere nden Й“aawo nde arii a am, Seytaane laatike ko o jaasinoowo neЙ—Й—anke on"
  25,30,"NulaaЙ—o on maaka: \"Ko ann yo Jooma pellet, yimЙ“e am Й“en Й“e jogitike ndee Alqur'aanaare wikkaande(accaande)"
  25,31,"Ko wano nii, Men waЙ—irani kala Annabaajo gaГұo immorde e bonЙ“e Й“en, Joomi maaЙ—a yonii Fewnoowo e Ballo"
  25,32,"ЖҒen yedduЙ“e wi'i: \"Ko hanno Alqur'aanaare nden jippinee e makko e jumla gooto?\" ЖҠum ko wano nii, fii yo Men tabintinir nde Й“ernde maaЙ—a nden Men rewnindira nde rewnindirgol"
  25,33,"ЖҒe addantaa ma misal, si wanaa Men addanii ma Goonga kan e ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude firo"
  25,34,"ЖҒen mooЙ“oyteeЙ“e e dow geece muuЙ—um faade ka Jahannama, ko Й“en Й—on woni Й“uruЙ“e bonde nokkuure e Й“uruЙ“e majjude kade laawol"
  25,35,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, Men waЙ—i wonndude e makko MusiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna ballo"
  25,36,"Men Daali: \"Yahee ka Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Men yirbini Й“e yirbinndee"
  25,37,"E yimЙ“e Nuuhu tuma nde Й“e fennunoo NulaaЙ“e Й“en, Men yooli Й“e Men waЙ—i Й“e maande fii yimЙ“e Й“en, Men heblani tooГұooЙ“e Й“en Lepte muusuЙ—e"
  25,38,E AadinkooЙ“e Й“en e SamuudinkooЙ“e Й“en e yimЙ“e Й“unndu ndun e gire Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e hakkunde Й—um
  25,39,"Gooto kala e maЙ“e Men piyani Й—um mise, gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e men halki Й—um halkugol"
  25,40,"GomЙ—ii Й“e arii e nden saare toЙ“aande toЙ“o bonngo. Kaa Й“e laataaki hiЙ“e yi'a Й—e? Ko woni, Й“e laatinoke Й“e jortaaki Immotal"
  25,41,"Si Й“e yi'ii ma, Й“e jogitotaako ma si wanaa jalnori. Enee, ko oo Alla Immini NulaaЙ—o"
  25,42,Fii kala hari o Й“adike(Й—esi) majjinnde en gaayi reweteeЙ—i me'en Й—in si tawiino wanaa ko muГұГұi Й—en kon e dow majji. Aray Й“e anndoyat tuma Й“e yi'ata Lepte Й—en ko hommbo Й“urЙ—o majjude laawol
  25,43,"Enee, a tinii on jogitiiЙ—o reweteeЙ—o makko on beleeЙ—e makko Й—en. E hara ko an laatotoo e dow makko fawtiiЙ—o"
  25,44,"Kaa a sikku wonnde ko Й“uri heewude e maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e nana maaЙ—um hiЙ“e hakkila? Anndu kamЙ“e Й“e wonaali si wanaa wano neemoraaЙ—i, toode, ko kamЙ“e Й“uri majjude laawol"
  25,45,"Kaa a tinaali faade e Joomi maaЙ—a honno O fontiri Й—owdi ndin? Sinndo O Muuyuno O waЙ—ayno ndi deeЖҙundi, refti Men waЙ—i naange ngen tinndinaynge e mayri"
  25,46,Refti Men tami ndi ka Amen tamannde newiinde
  25,47,"Ko Kanko woni On waЙ—anЙ—o on jemma on koltu e Й—oyngol ngol fowtere, O waЙ—i Гұalorma on ngal saakorЙ—o"
  25,48,"Ko Kanko woni On accituЙ—o keni Й—in ko Й—i weltinooji hakkunde Yurmeende Makko nden, Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam laaЙ“uЙ—am"
  25,49,"Fii yo Men wurnitir Й—am leydi maayundi, Men yarnaЙ—am kadi kon ko Men tagi neemoraaЙ—i e yimЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e"
  25,50,"GomЙ—ii Men fensitii nde hakkunde maЙ“Й“e fii yo Й“e waajito, salii Й“urЙ“e Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en si wanaa yeddugol"
  25,51,Sinndo Men Muuyuno Men Nulayno e kala saare jertinoowo
  25,52,Wata a Й—ofto yedduЙ“e Й“en haЙ“ e maЙ“Й“e hare jihaadi mawnde